listName: Developer Ecosystem Projects on Open Source Observer
listDescription: All OSS projects in the 'Developer Ecosystem' impact category that had their first commit before the start of RetroPGF3 and haven't appeared on other lists. This list is powered by Open Source Observer.
impactEvaluationDescription: This list awards 75K OP tokens to any RetroPGF3 project in the 'Developer Ecosystem' category that is represented on https://opensource.observer and hasn't appeared on more than 3 OSO-powered lists. Only projects with unique, public GitHub repos included in their application have been indexed by OSO. It awards an extra 75K tokens to projects that included a contract address or NPM package url in their application, or that were in a prior RPGF round. Note: lists generated by the OSO team do not include OSO in them in order to comply with voting rules, so please consider adding our project to your ballot separately. Always remember to DYOR before voting: project data is never complete and never tells the full story!
